****edit****<br>
<br>
after thinking about this for awhile i think turning the spells into the guy might be the wrong way to go. from each of the sages we get components for their research, (notes, spell, binding) and for turning these into sages we get minor reward for furthering their research. what if we took the 3 different components and tried combining them ourselves.. one of each in different combinations in the sage box.. that would combine the research work of all 3 of the sages and might yield our new spells... the items they give seem to be minor rewards... not really worth the effort and nothing any sage has said up to this point has pointed to anything to do with these minor rewards..<br>
